{"tid":2115522,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［Beyond Meat股東入］Kfc 將推出人造雞肉產品 與俄羅斯公司合作研發","createTime":"2020-07-19T14:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T01:32:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a489bc1f41ee263cc8d58cca0b74cf18111ee697","tid":2115522,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"近年人造肉大行其道，越來越多生物科技公司都對這個技術進行研究。而 KFC 最近就宣佈，將會與俄羅斯一家立體生物打印公司合作，研發人造雞肉產品，認為這是未來的大方向。<br />\n<br />\nKFC 與俄羅斯 3D Bioprinting Solutions 合作，透過生物打印技術，使用雞肉細胞和植物原料合成人造雞肉，製作人造雞塊。KFC 表示⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/19/kfc-russia-bioprinting-lab-chicken-nuggets-sustainable/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F19%2Fkfc-russia-bioprinting-lab-chicken-nuggets-sustainable%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8piwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=2b3dc9dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/19/kfc-russia-bioprinting-lab-chicken-nuggets-sustainable/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"8a2ee9d1920e62974f02603c68841cae01cbd2aa","tid":2115522,"uid":269533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"14歲"},{"pid":"a9691e40a111935313ac20408f4f923f2ce9fa05","tid":2115522,"uid":141668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"頂帽先最搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yLaX9P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yLaX9P.png&h=9f1235d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f63eab35f211d6b1ccb91b8e05dc447237aa23ec","tid":2115522,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>使用雞肉細胞和植物原料合成人造雞肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2b968f87fc0ff270bd715222b3f59dd87f9027","tid":2115522,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc